TITLE: Initializing Cluster Sharding for an Entity Type in Scala
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to initialize Akka Cluster Sharding for a specific entity type (`Counter`) in Scala. This setup registers the entity type and its behavior factory with the sharding extension.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akka/akka/blob/main/akka-docs/src/main/paradox/typed/cluster-sharding.md#2025-04-22_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
import akka.cluster.sharding.typed.scaladsl.Entity
import akka.cluster.sharding.typed.scaladsl.EntityTypeKey

val TypeKey = EntityTypeKey[Counter.Command]("Counter")

// #init
val shardRegion: ActorRef[ShardingEnvelope[Counter.Command]] = sharding.init(Entity(TypeKey)(
  createBehavior = entityContext =>
    Counter(entityContext.entityId)
))
// #init
