TITLE: Implementing MyReadJournal in Scala
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to implement a custom ReadJournal plugin in Scala that supports EventsByTagQuery. It demonstrates the implementation of both scaladsl and javadsl interfaces, with the javadsl implementation delegating to the scaladsl one.
