LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
final case class MovieWatchList(
    userId: String,
    movies: ORSet[String] = ORSet.empty) {

  def add(movieId: String): MovieWatchList =
    copy(movies = movies.add(ReplicaId.random, movieId))

  def remove(movieId: String): MovieWatchList =
    copy(movies = movies.remove(movieId))

  def contains(movieId: String): Boolean =
    movies.elements.contains(movieId)
}
```

