TITLE: Implementing a Multi-Node Test Specification in Scala
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates a complete multi-node test that initializes two nodes, uses a barrier for synchronization, and tests actor message passing between nodes. It includes environment setup, node identification, and remote messaging.
