TITLE: Combining Tick with ZipLatest in Java
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates combining Source.tick with zipLatest in Java to periodically update values in a stream.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akka/akka/blob/main/akka-docs/src/main/paradox/stream/operators/Source/tick.md#2025-04-22_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
Source<Pair<T, Response>, NotUsed> streamWithUpdatingValue(ActorRef<Query> actor) {
  Source<Response, NotUsed> responseStream =
      Source.tick(Duration.ZERO, Duration.ofSeconds(1), "tick")
          .mapAsync(
              1,
              tick ->
                  Patterns.ask(
                          actor, Query::new, Duration.ofSeconds(3), system.scheduler())
                      .thenApply(Response.class::cast));

  return elements.zipLatest(responseStream);
}
```

