TITLE: EventStream Superclass Subscription in Java
DESCRIPTION: Java code showing how to subscribe to a group of events by subscribing to their common superclass on the event stream. This allows receiving multiple related event types with a single subscription.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akka/akka/blob/main/akka-docs/src/main/paradox/event-bus.md#2025-04-22_snippet_28

LANGUAGE: Java
CODE:
```
// common superclass or trait
public static class AllKindsOfMusic {
  public final String artist;

  public AllKindsOfMusic(String artist) {
    this.artist = artist;
  }
}

public static class Jazz extends AllKindsOfMusic {
  public Jazz(String artist) {
    super(artist);
  }
}

public static class Electronic extends AllKindsOfMusic {
  public Electronic(String artist) {
    super(artist);
  }
}

ActorRef musicListener =
    system.actorOf(
        Props.create(
            AbstractActor.class,
            () ->
                new AbstractActor() {
                  @Override
                  public Receive createReceive() {
                    return receiveBuilder()
                        .match(
                            Jazz.class,
                            msg -> {
                              System.out.println(
                                  getSelf().path().name()
                                      + " is listening to: "
                                      + msg.artist);
                            })
                        .match(
                            Electronic.class,
                            msg -> {
                              System.out.println(
                                  getSelf().path().name()
                                      + " is listening to: "
                                      + msg.artist);
                            })
                        .match(
                            AllKindsOfMusic.class,
                            msg -> {
                              System.out.println(
                                  getSelf().path().name()
                                      + " heard some music but didn't recognize what kind it is");
                            })
                        .build();
                  }
                }));

system.getEventStream().subscribe(musicListener, AllKindsOfMusic.class);

system.eventEventStream().publish(new Electronic("Parov Stelar"));
```

