DESCRIPTION: Provides the basic structure of the DeviceGroupQuery actor, including initialization and message handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akka/akka/blob/main/akka-docs/src/main/paradox/typed/guide/tutorial_5.md#2025-04-22_snippet_1

