TITLE: Sorting Elements to Multiple Groups with groupBy in Akka Streams
DESCRIPTION: This pattern allows mapping elements to multiple groups simultaneously, unlike the standard groupBy which puts each element in exactly one group. It's useful for scenarios like message routing to multiple topics.
SOURCE: https://github.com/akka/akka/blob/main/akka-docs/src/main/paradox/stream/stream-cookbook.md#2025-04-22_snippet_28

LANGUAGE: Scala
CODE:
