LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
EntityTypeKey<CounterCommand> TypeKey = EntityTypeKey.create(CounterCommand.class, "Counter");

ActorRef<ShardingEnvelope<CounterCommand>> shardRegion =
    ClusterSharding.get(system)
        .init(
            Entity.of(
                    TypeKey,
                    entityContext -> counter(entityContext.getShard(), entityContext.getEntityId()))
                // specify the GoodByeCounter message adapts the ShardCommand to the CounterCommand
                // but typically you would have a dedicated stop message
                .withStopMessageAdapter(shardCommand -> new GoodByeCounter(shardCommand.entityId())));
```

