TITLE: Demonstrating Version Compatibility in Akka Scala
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet illustrates the binary compatibility rules for Akka versions, showing which version upgrades are allowed and which are not. It covers both the old epoch.major.minor era and the new major.minor.patch era.
