SOURCE: https://github.com/akka/akka/blob/main/akka-docs/src/main/paradox/io-udp.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: scala
CODE:
```
class Connected extends Actor {
  IO(Udp) ! Connect(self, remote)
  def receive = {
    case Connected =>
      context.become(ready(sender()))
  }
  def ready(connection: ActorRef): Receive = {
    case data: ByteString =>
      connection ! Send(data)
    case Received(data) =>
      // process data...
    case CommandFailed(w: Send) =>
      // handle failed send
  }
}
```

