LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
Source<Response, NotUsed> queryActor(ActorRef<Query> actor) {
  return Source.tick(Duration.ZERO, Duration.ofSeconds(1), "tick")
      .mapAsync(1, tick -> Patterns.ask(actor, Query::new, Duration.ofSeconds(3), system.scheduler())
          .thenApply(Response.class::cast));
}
